{
  "name": "wukong",
  "counters": [
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "wukong",
      "description": "here i'll just tell you what you can do and what the enemy can do. for more detailed information, visit \"detailed matchups\"."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "akali",
      "description": "she can hit you with e and q during your e. she is also stronger during her w, so back off. you should conduct short trades e+w+q, then you can go all in. if you have a reaction, then you can stop her e and r with r, then she will not run away from you and will die."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "aurora",
      "description": "she deals a lot of ap damage and can kite you easily. wait for lvl 6 and one shot her, but you must interrupt her w with r or she'll just run away. don't try to kill her without r."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "cassiopeia",
      "description": "she can use w and r during your e, so she'll kill you. kill her on lvl 2 or 3. after lvl 6 wait for her mistakes and all in."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "cho'gath",
      "description": "he can use w during your e. use w to evade his q. trade after his q. use long trades."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "gragas",
      "description": "his e counters you. buy ravenous hydra and keep farming."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "illaoi",
      "description": "she can abuse your w to heal from it. use w to evade her e and then all in her."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "jax",
      "description": "he can ignore your q with e. he can zone you from farming with q. use w to evade his e. stay in bush and get exp. you can all in him after lvl 6."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "kayle",
      "description": "you have to kill her before lvl 6. keep freezing and abuse her weakness."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "kennen",
      "description": "you can use w to evade his q. he can easily trade with you, don't use e until he spends q! use w to evade his r."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "lee sin",
      "description": "he is much stronger than you, so just wait for the moment when he spends his abilities on minions, then you can go to trade. after 6 you can't go all in because of his r. use r to interrupt his q or w."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "malphite",
      "description": "unplayable, his abilities counter you. afk farm."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "mordekaiser",
      "description": "he can use q and e during your e. use e+aa+q+w combo for short trades. use w to evade his q. you can kill him after lvl 6 if he's low hp and you're high hp."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "neeko",
      "description": "she can use e during your e. she'll use w after your e. you can't initiate, you're useless. try to farm."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "ornn",
      "description": "he can use his abilities during your e. use r to interrupt his e or r. try to farm, you overscale him."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "pantheon",
      "description": "he'll poke you with q. he'll use w during your e. he'll use e when you're going to trade. wait for lvl 6 and try to interrupt his w with r, then you can kill him."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "poppy",
      "description": "she will use e during your e, so don't use that to approach, use w for that. wait for her to spend passive on a minion so as not to be poked. after 6, use r to interrupt her e or r, and also w to evade her r."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "renekton",
      "description": "he's just stronger than you. try to farm and kill him if he dives you. you can interrupt his e with r."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "rumble",
      "description": "among all the ap matchups, this is the most difficult one, nothing will help you against it. however, i'm not banning him just because he's unpopular. he has more damage and survivability. he'll push the wave towards you and poke you with q and e, so, try to dodge it and farm."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "sejuani",
      "description": "you can't beat her. she'll use q to interrupt your e. try to farm. use r to interrupt her q."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "shyvana",
      "description": "try to dodge her e and farm, you can't kill her if you're poked and you will be poked!"
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "swain",
      "description": "he has a lot of damage. use w to evade his e. one shot him on lvl 6."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "sylas",
      "description": "he has a lot of damage. use w to evade his e. use r to interrupt his e. one shot him on lvl 6."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "tahm kench",
      "description": "use w to evade his q or w. use r to interrupt his w. just farm, you can't kill him."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "trundle",
      "description": "try to farm. you can't kill him if he has r. poke him and kill then."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "udyr",
      "description": "he's very tanky and annoying, buy ravenous hydra and just farm."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "vladimir",
      "description": "he can heal from your clone with q. all in him or die!"
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "volibear",
      "description": "renekton 2.0, personal permaban."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "warwick",
      "description": "you can't damage him (because of his healing), just try to farm."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "yasuo",
      "description": "he can use e on your clone. use w to evade his q. use r to interrupt his e and one shot him. he can kite you with e, then he'll kill you."
    },
    {
      "type": "extreme",
      "champName": "yone",
      "description": "use w to evade his q. you can't kill him because he can easily evade your damage with q/w/e/r (xd, with any ability!)."
    },
    {
      "type": "major",
      "champName": "zac",
      "description": "use w to evade his e. use r to interrupt his e."
    }
  ],
